40|$|The aim of {{the article}} is to {{evaluate}} <b>the</b> <b>European</b> <b>Central</b> <b>Bank’s</b> activity in <b>the</b> context of the fulfilment of the price stability criterion by the euro area Member States. The paper {{is divided into two}} major parts. The first part focuses on the Theory of Optimum Currency Areas with particular emphasis on price stability. The second part contains an attempt to assess <b>the</b> <b>European</b> <b>Central</b> <b>Bank’s</b> anti-inflationary monetary policy in the euro area...|$|R
